::Battera::

She went straight to her room.  She opened the door walked inside.
She turned and looked at Rex for a moment, then turned and shut the 
door behind her. 

She walked over to her bed and layed down.  She wanted to go and fly. 
To be free from all the war and hatred and to just be happy.  She 
hoped that one day, she would be free.
